Here is the student and their Q/A array:
Student: {{$json.studentName}}
File: {{$json.fileName}}
Questions: {{$json.questions}}

For each question produce: question_id, score (integer 0-10), feedback (1-2 sentences). Also include an overall_summary and total_score. Return a single JSON object: {"results": [...], "total_score": 76, "overall_summary": "..." }

